How can you count in Java?
To count in java you use an operator called increment operator.
How can you check to see if a number is divisible?
Even numbers are divisible by 2 and this is the Divisibilty by 2 rule there are also the Divisibility by 3,4,5,6,8,9,10,11 rules if a number can not be divided by one of these then it is not divisible

